  "text": "The limitation of formulae (4.8) and (4.9) is that the power series involved are supposed to converge only for |x| < 1. A more convenient representation of the conformal block was developed by Al. Zamolodchikov in [CITATION_1] , where he proposed to regard the block as a function of the variable",
